2. In `WhatsAppService.gs`, implement `sendWhatsAppNotification(message, phone)` using placeholder behavior.
3. If token is missing, log a warning and return a failure result without throwing.
4. Ensure the order save still succeeds even when WhatsApp send fails.
Acceptance criteria:
